import math

def main():
    A, B, C, D = map(int, input().split())
    ans = B - A + 1
    ans -= math.floor(B / C) - math.floor((A - 1) / C)
    ans -= math.floor(B / D) - math.floor((A - 1) / D)
    ans += math.floor(B / (C * D)) - math.floor((A - 1) / (C * D))
    print(ans)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
